   Goldsmith Ends Attempt to Buy B.A.T
   Amid Public Worries on Leveraged Bids
   ----
   By Richard E. Rustin
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/24/90
</DATE>
